Cell.Data: A set of images produced in single study (one or more series of references images)
Reference IHE radiology TF vol 2 table 4.14.1
Manifest of a set of images produced in study. The set of images may include every image in the study, or it may be an incomplete sample, such as a list of key images
Date and Time the study took place
Order(s) that caused this study to be performed
A list of the diagnostic orders that resulted in this imaging study being performed
To support grouped procedures (one imaging study supporting multiple ordered procedures, e.g., chest/abdomen/pelvis CT)

The order(s) can be inferred from information such as accession numbers, but the details of this depend on local workflow management. Note that there is a many-many relationship between orders and studies
